metadata.name: Miss Sun-Spring
metadata.description:
Miss Sun's arts are inspired by the women's day from ancient Persia. In ancient Persia, there was a day known for appreciating and thanking women, known as "Women's Day." 
Character Attribute 
Lady With The Scarf: Name Is Spring 
Personality: Courageous, Smart, Influencer
Scarf : Light Pink, silk fabric flourish patterns.
Dress: Long Sleeves Light Purple Kashmir, silk wave patterns 
Hooka: Hand made, Citrine, Lemon Quartz, plated gold patterns 
Background: Magical nature, Miss Sun Shining. All four elements of the nature Earth, Air, Fire, Water
Eye Color: Honey Brown
Hair Color: Dark Brown
Eyebrow: Unibrow, regarded as symbols of good luck
Background Music: Swanee River
Type: Animated
